WEBVTT

00:01.069 --> 00:02.636
**

00:02.703 --> 00:03.904
Twilight: As you've
all probably noticed,

00:03.971 --> 00:06.707
it's been quite some time
since the map has sent us

00:06.774 --> 00:08.342
on a mission of friendship.

00:08.409 --> 00:10.278
Yeah, ever since
Starlight messed with it

00:10.344 --> 00:12.746
to go back in time and
tried to change history.

00:12.813 --> 00:16.217
Yes. Since then. But
as part of her studies,

00:16.284 --> 00:18.119
Starlight's been
assisting me

00:18.186 --> 00:20.221
and together we think
we've come up with a spell

00:20.288 --> 00:21.722
that will get it
working again.

00:21.789 --> 00:23.391
Woo-hoo! Oooh!
Well done!

00:25.693 --> 00:27.161
Now, without further ado...

00:30.931 --> 00:36.370
[whoosh]

00:37.705 --> 00:40.408
Everyone: Oooh!

00:40.474 --> 00:42.410
Fluttershy and
Twilight in Appleoosa!

00:42.476 --> 00:44.645
NO! Me and Rainbow
Dash in Las Pegasus!

00:44.712 --> 00:46.814
NO! Rainbow Dash and
Twilight in Yakyakistan!

00:46.880 --> 00:49.483
NO! TWILIGHT AND TWILIGHT IN
TWILIGHT'S CASTLE!? [gasp]

00:49.550 --> 00:52.186
ME! ME! OH! ME!

00:52.253 --> 00:55.389
AND RARITY! Oooooh I hope
it's some faraway place

00:55.456 --> 00:57.825
that nopony has
gone before!

00:57.891 --> 01:01.829
[laugh] Well. [chuckle]
Maybe not TOO far away.

01:01.895 --> 01:04.198
An adventure somewhere that
has modern conveniences

01:04.265 --> 01:06.167
would be preferable.

01:06.234 --> 01:09.470
[gasp] CANTERLOT! [gasp]
This is wonderful!

01:09.537 --> 01:10.671
I can check the boutique!

01:10.738 --> 01:12.206
Perhaps there will
be some social events

01:12.273 --> 01:13.407
that we can attend!

01:13.474 --> 01:14.642
[gasp] I'll have to
pack extra outfits!

01:14.708 --> 01:17.445
What will I wear!

01:17.511 --> 01:19.313
You know, some
ponies get excited

01:19.380 --> 01:21.149
about the
silliest things.

01:24.652 --> 01:27.921
* My little pony,
my little pony *

01:27.988 --> 01:29.890
* Aaaahhh *

01:29.957 --> 01:31.559
* My little Pony *

01:31.625 --> 01:34.528
* I used to wonder what
friendship could be. *

01:34.595 --> 01:36.297
* My Little Pony *

01:36.364 --> 01:38.832
* Until you all shared
its magic with me. *

01:38.899 --> 01:40.634
* Big adventure! *
* Tons of fun *

01:40.701 --> 01:42.470
* A beautiful heart! * *
Faithful and strong! *

01:42.536 --> 01:45.173
* Sharing kindness *
* it's an easy feat *

01:45.239 --> 01:47.408
** And magic makes it
all complete! *

01:47.475 --> 01:49.510
* To have my little pony *

01:49.577 --> 01:52.813
* Do you know you're all
my very best friends? *

01:52.880 --> 01:55.349
**

02:00.354 --> 02:04.892
**

02:04.958 --> 02:08.329
[sigh] Now then. As far as
finding a friendship problem,

02:08.396 --> 02:10.364
I suggest we start
at the castle

02:10.431 --> 02:11.699
and begin to
question the proper--

02:11.765 --> 02:14.468
Oh, Rarity, you don't
find a friendship problem.

02:14.535 --> 02:17.571
It finds you! We just
need to go with the flow

02:17.638 --> 02:19.773
and eventually KABLAM! We
get friendship problem'd

02:19.840 --> 02:21.575
right between
the eyes!

02:21.642 --> 02:23.811
Well, this is a
team effort

02:23.877 --> 02:25.979
so if you feel we
should go with the flow,

02:26.046 --> 02:28.716
then with the flow
we shall go!

02:28.782 --> 02:31.485
Where is the flow
saying we should go?

02:31.552 --> 02:34.322
You know Canterlot! What
do you think we should do?

02:34.388 --> 02:37.491
Oh! Take your pick!
Culture, couture, cuisine!

02:37.558 --> 02:39.560
[rumbling]

02:41.529 --> 02:43.664
Oh my. Well, it sounds
like your stomach

02:43.731 --> 02:46.300
