flow towards some lunch?

02:46.367 --> 02:47.668
I know JUST where to go!

02:49.570 --> 02:51.004
Restaurant Row!

02:51.071 --> 02:53.241
The absolute best
place for fine dining

02:53.307 --> 02:54.842
in all of Equestria.

02:54.908 --> 02:57.345
Ooooooh, so many choices!

02:57.411 --> 03:00.414
