has been marinated overnight

05:23.190 --> 05:25.426
in a mustard
Dijon dressing.

05:25.493 --> 05:27.395
How can we say
no to that?

05:27.461 --> 05:28.696
A-And for you?

05:28.762 --> 05:30.631
Oh! Me? Oh, I'm
fine. Thank you.

05:31.865 --> 05:33.601
No rating.

05:34.868 --> 05:38.005
[sigh] [Mumbling]
Anyway they won't come.

05:38.071 --> 05:39.840
Hiya! What's your name?

05:39.907 --> 05:41.709
Coriander Cumin.

05:41.775 --> 05:43.076
Are you a chef here, too?

05:43.143 --> 05:45.746
My daughter cooks. I host.

05:45.813 --> 05:47.848
Then why are you
stacking chairs?

05:47.915 --> 05:52.986
Without customers, I have no
pony to host for. So, I stack.

05:53.053 --> 05:54.321
Father! STOP IT!

05:54.388 --> 05:57.558
