around our guests!

05:57.625 --> 05:59.627
What does it matter?
When they leave,

05:59.693 --> 06:02.195
nopony else will
be coming in!

06:02.262 --> 06:05.833
Well, your attitude isn't
going to bring anyone in!

06:05.899 --> 06:08.802
Can't you at least
pretend to be positive?

06:08.869 --> 06:13.474
[slurp] Sooooooo
goooooood! [gobbles]

06:13.541 --> 06:16.510
Father: You are doing enough
pretending for the both of us.

06:16.577 --> 06:20.180
Nopony here wants
to try anything new.

06:20.247 --> 06:22.850
I know when to
throw in the towel!

06:22.916 --> 06:25.886
Um. Pinkie, perhaps we
should excuse ourselves.

06:25.953 --> 06:29.757
[chews] Oh Rarity,
try this!

06:29.823 --> 06:32.860
[gulps] Oooh!

06:32.926 --> 06:35.996
Maybe if you would listen
to my ideas for once--

06:36.063 --> 06:39.567
Oh yes, I did not move
halfway across Equestria

06:39.633 --> 06:43.070
for my daughter that
I NEVER listen to!

06:43.136 --> 06:45.138
Rarity. I think that
friendship problem

06:45.205 --> 06:47.808
just KABLAMMED us
right between the eyes.

06:47.875 --> 06:51.044
These two? Oh I
don't know, darling.

06:51.111 --> 06:54.047
The food IS excellent, but
I'm not sure there's much

06:54.114 --> 06:56.650
