even worth rating!

07:05.192 --> 07:06.794
THAT'S IT!

07:06.860 --> 07:09.897
YES! Uh, what's it?

07:09.963 --> 07:13.033
The flow HAS led us here!
THIS is our mission!

07:13.100 --> 07:15.636
We are going to get
you a Three Hoof rating

07:15.703 --> 07:20.007
and save your restaurant! I
can get Zesty Gourmand here.

07:20.073 --> 07:22.943
[gasp] And I can pack
this place with ponies!

07:23.010 --> 07:25.946
Hmph! And how do you
intend to do such a thing?

07:26.013 --> 07:27.781
Just leave it to us!

07:35.188 --> 07:38.759
Father, will you PLEASE
stop packing things?

07:38.826 --> 07:40.761
When the lovely
pony comes back

07:40.828 --> 07:43.263
