know Rarity.

07:50.838 --> 07:53.006
I've done it!

07:53.073 --> 07:54.608
See?

07:54.675 --> 07:56.644
It took all of my
charm and cajoling,

07:56.710 --> 07:58.946
but I was able to
convince Zesty Gourmand

07:59.012 --> 08:00.681
to come and try the food!

08:00.748 --> 08:02.850
What is the catch?

08:02.916 --> 08:07.254
Ah, yes. Well, um, there
IS a bit of a challenge.

08:07.320 --> 08:10.724
The only time she can make
herself available is tonight.

08:10.791 --> 08:12.760
Pfft! Oh yeah, right.

08:12.826 --> 08:13.861
What is it?

08:13.927 --> 08:16.163
Zesty rates a restaurant
on cuisine, decor

08:16.229 --> 08:20.233
AND presentation. And she
has very specific tastes.

08:20.300 --> 08:22.703
