to help our friends

13:10.157 --> 13:12.592
by getting them three hooves.
That will only happen

13:12.659 --> 13:14.361
if this IS like every
other restaurant.

13:16.463 --> 13:19.332
Father, what is this?

13:19.399 --> 13:23.070
NOT THAT! ANYTHING BUT THAT!

13:23.136 --> 13:26.974
