Everypony! Places!

14:14.021 --> 14:16.623
Welcome to the Tasty Treat.

14:16.689 --> 14:19.159
What can I get you
this evening?

14:19.226 --> 14:21.094
I hardly think it matters.

14:21.161 --> 14:24.998
But by all means, try
your best to impress.

14:25.065 --> 14:27.167
Well, we'll both try the
special this evening,

14:27.234 --> 14:29.202
maybe with a little
kick to it, eh?

14:29.269 --> 14:31.438
Yeah, we've been craving
some food with actual taste.

14:35.442 --> 14:38.278
